Commentary Text: Shreyas Gopal to Dhawan, out Caught by Kartik Tyagi!! Gopal has broken the partnership. Dhawan had decided it was time to up the ante but plays the most un-Dhawan-like shot. It was the front of the hand slider drifted across off, Dhawan goes for the reverse hit/ switch hit, the ball balloons of the top-edge and Tyagi tracks back from short third to take the catch.
